🥦 we all love to get high

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by AFTER I GOT HIGH in Seattle, Washington. May be an image of text that says 'AFTER GOT HIGH post #262 After I got high, I was gonna send a message to this page about a story I had, but I fell asleep and woke up and forgot the story.'.

Photo by AFTER I GOT HIGH in Seattle, Washington. May be an image of text that says 'AFTER GOT HIGH post #261 After I got high, I had a really cool plan for a weekend with my friends, emailed myself so I wouldn't forget. The next day I saw saw the email and it said "email yourself that idea so you don't forget".'.

node.text:
High ideas are the best ideas🤣

node.text: Muscle memory💨 Keep sending in After I Got High stories so I have more funny ones to share

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by AFTER I GOT HIGH on August 20, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'AFTER GOT HIGH post #259 After I got high, I ordered 500 "After I Got High" flags thinking everyone would want one but only 25 people bought them.'.

node.text:
I can laugh about it now, but I’m not going to lie I was pretty butt hurt about it for a few weeks, but y’all reminded me that this whole thing is just another After I Got High story. 

I truly enjoy running this account and this community so it’s time to get this thing going again. Also, if you want a flag they are available on my website!

Photo by AFTER I GOT HIGH on August 20, 2021. May be an image of nature.

Photo by AFTER I GOT HIGH in Boston, Massachusetts. May be an image of text that says 'AFTER GOT HIGH post #258 After I got high, I was in the garage with my guy friends and one disappeared We searched everywhere only for him to come running back, soaked head to toe. Turns out he got thirsty so instead of asking us for a water bottle from the case he went and drank from our neighbors hose.'.

node.text: We are back!! If you sent in this story, DM me to receive your prize. Make sure to send in your funniest stories each week for a chance to win!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by AFTER I GOT HIGH in Planet 13. May be an image of text that says 'AFTER GOT HIGH post #257 After| got high I was smoking outside at my dad's house trying to hide it in my car, finished smoking and went back inside. Next morning went out to smoke again, I had left my trunk and doors open all night long.'.

node.text:
That's one way of keeping your car from smelling😂

node.text:
‼️Hey guys, I am excited to announce that tomorrow @4:20 pm EST we will be having our first merch drop. We will be selling After I Got High flags (they are 3x5 ft) and will cost $18.‼️
